lines.text:
[to the Warlock]
How did you get past my secretary?
Do not give him the stone. He is E-vil!
Ah, so you really are psychic?

[first line of his resurrection]
Won't you give your boy a kiss, Mother?
I'm not a *man*, I am a witch.
When I look at a fool, I see a mirror... But when I look in a mirror, I see a fool!
Mirror mirror on the wall, who's the scaredest one of all?
